      "parameters": {
        "content": "# ⚖️ Enterprise Legal Compliance Auditor\n**Asset ID:** TWA-LEG-2026-V1  \n**Target:** 2026 ADM & Privacy Act Regulatory Audits  \n**Core Engine:** n8n + Google Gemini API + Google Sheets  \n**Built By:** The Workflow Atelier\n\n---\n### 💡 What This Blueprint Achieves\nAutomatically inspects incoming vendor agreements and contracts for regulatory compliance gaps, outputting structured risk data to an executive reporting dashboard in seconds.",
        "height": 352,
        "width": 688,
        "color": 6
